text: The flag of the Commonwealth of the Northern Mariana Islands features a star (representing the United States), a latte stone (representing the Chamorros), and a mwarmwar (wreath; represents the Carolinians). These symbols are all on a blue background which represents the Pacific Ocean and the Mariana Trench. The flag was adopted in 1985. == Gallery == == Related articles == * Northern Mariana Islands * Seal of the Northern Mariana Islands * Flags of the U.S. states and territories Category:Northern Mariana Islands Category:United States territory flags
